  "title": "Admissions Aboard the Angry Rancor",
  "summary": "While traveling aboard the luxury cruise ship Angry Rancor, the Corellian freighter pilot Markus Lisardis and his companion Simon both wander into the ship's Wampa Lounge, unsettled by its cages of captive exotic animals. Their chance meeting turns into a deep philosophical conversation as Simon explains the True Source of Life and reveals that he is a Selas, one born with an unsevered connection to that power, which his people regard as a curse. Simon confides his suspicion that Markus shares this same gift, comparing the Selas to the Jedi and recounting the violence and honor entwined in his people's history. Markus receives the news with stoic curiosity rather than fear, refusing to accept that the connection is inherently evil. The two part with much to contemplate, anticipating that their coming meeting with the Jedi Luke Skywalker will bring further clarity.",
